                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d398">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/4835: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-01-26T13:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 26, 1923—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 26—9:37 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Consul at Canton telegraphs Hu Han-min, sympathizer of Sun Yat-sen,
                    inaugurated civil governor yesterday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Schurman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
